The paper deals with the problem of multi-image alignment, which is a common problem in computer vision and image processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses statistical models and lower bounds, which suggests that it may belong to cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Additionally, the paper deals with performance limits, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.LG (Machine Learning).
